data.description:
Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this two-story residence presents a blend of modern convenience and outdoor enjoyment. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers a spacious and functional layout. As you step through the front door, you're immediately greeted by an open and inviting atmosphere. The master is located on the lower level. Enjoy the backyard fire pit & playground!
Solar Panels will be removed prior to closing. Painting Allowance offered as well.
